{"tid":535762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英癌妻死前囑丈夫淋花 淋咗幾年先發現係膠嘅喂！","createTime":"2018-01-21T08:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T20:01:05.000Z","uid":36494,"like":1222,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":100,"replies":[{"pid":"8c7515d2d1731fa835bf990e765a12ba0ecabe6e","tid":535762,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T08:05:38.000Z","msg":"一名來自英國的患癌婦人得知自己時日無多，千叮萬嚀要丈夫記得為她種的植物澆水。她離世後，丈夫果然悉心灌溉，數年後想將它們搬到新家照料，卻驚訝萬分地發現這些「植物」原來是塑膠的。兩人的女兒在網上分享這件事，大讚媽媽幽默感過人，亦令家人覺得她仍在身邊。<br />\n<br />\n倫敦女消防員尼科爾（Antonia Nicol）近日在Twitter上發文寫道：「我媽媽離世前曾留下嚴格指示，要我爸爸為浴室內的植物澆水。他自此定期為它們澆水灌溉，讓其得以繼續生長。它們很漂亮，令他決定將它們搬到他的新家，但他卻發現它們是塑膠造的！我似乎能聽到媽媽正在咯咯地笑。」<br />\n<br />\n尼科爾的母親菲頓（Phedre Fitton）於2013年11月死於癌症，終年69歲。尼科爾憶述時指，她媽媽抵抗癌魔5年後離世，當時全家人都很難過，相信媽媽死前交付「重任」給爸爸，是想讓他「有事可做」，度過傷心難過的日子。<br />\n<br />\n她說︰「當我爸爸發現自己數年來在為塑膠植物澆水時，我們所有人都覺得很惹笑，也覺得她（媽媽）仍然陪伴著我們。」她的帖文在網上引起關注後，爸爸還很配合地「重演」他平時淋花的動作。<br />\n<br />\n尼科爾形容媽媽生前是個非常幽默的人，又透露她的父母早於16歲時已相識，結伴走過許多年，但如今卻未能一起度過晚年生活，難免令人遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180121&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=57732254\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180121%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D57732254&d=QaAlz3VG9psVBQmHWv3ogTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=58c112e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180121%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D57732254&h=47e1408d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180121&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=57732254</a><br />\n【笑中有淚】英癌妻死前囑丈夫淋花 淋咗幾年先發現係膠嘅喂！"},{"pid":"185d8dc6b9e89d60e0652fd52d36c540e22507eb","tid":535762,"uid":165023,"like":5,"dislike":43,"score":-38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T08:06:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5d0888fa436939c1f9dbfba37c8ba3163432f9","tid":535762,"uid":25916,"like":5,"dislike":43,"score":-38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T08:06:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a264855f8b3afc195e909c42ec3363e881a553cf","tid":535762,"uid":73356,"like":7,"dislike":44,"score":-37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T08:08:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e8bc6e088baa88cc638fd5f15adf27ae4d2ed70","tid":535762,"uid":36494,"like":1533,"dislike":7,"score":1526,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T08:09:11.000Z","msg":"如果係真花，枯萎咗之後個老公就無嘢可以寄託<br />\n<br />\n膠花可以長淋長有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88f408911876f8615822982a446c77736c389bce","tid":535762,"uid":79005,"like":621,"dislike":8,"score":613,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T08:10:01.000Z","msg":"唔係好感人咩 我差D想喊 點解樓上笑ge<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a8a09fc7c8e461501f19f12d909355d86444782","tid":535762,"uid":35846,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T08:10:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9279c770402bdfaf7bb8c9dddeb306f8f3978b6","tid":535762,"uid":76753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T08:10:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"295bf8a05d9da06d111b089c28f8d0646840a6ef","tid":535762,"uid":54927,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T08:10:52.000Z","msg":"有啲感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"398882f510ab1eaeef77c2c0a3d6b1fb3b84fe6c","tid":535762,"uid":42448,"like":122,"dislike":1,"score":121,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T08:11:13.000Z","msg":"見到「嘅喂」笑咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54a97ea162b0e937f3a295ca3701342b64c69e2a","tid":535762